      {"langtiles_doc":1,"text":"// yeti etc\ntheCompiledStuff(A,w) {\n    i hut/toot:3\n    o hut/toot$\n    let la = i hut/$toot\n    o hut/although:1,they,can,be,mixed\n    i $la/something\n    i thung/with/etc\n    i yeses/because,it:2\n    i yeses/because,it:5\n\n    [3]\n    S o yeses/because\n        let val = because.sc.it\n        i figiura/datch:$val\n    if 3\n        i know\n    if 0\n        i dont/know\n    elsif 1 && 0\n        && 50\n        i never/knew\n    elsif 50 > 5\n            && 3 > 2\n        i helped\n    i yep\n}\n"}
